AND YOU KNOW LONG-DISTANCE
RELATIONSHIPS, THEY NEVER WORK.

00:38.730 --> 00:40.539
AND FLORIDA AND CALIFORNIA,

00:40.570 --> 00:41.969
I MEAN, WE COULDN'T BE
FURTHER APART.

00:42.000 --> 00:45.800
- YEAH, I KNOW, BUT THIS TRIP
OUT HERE TOGETHER,

00:45.840 --> 00:48.877
IT'S MADE ME WANT TO THROW
CAUTION TO THE WIND, YOU KNOW?

