AND YOU--
YOU LIKE CALIFORNIA, RIGHT?

00:50.780 --> 00:54.113
- I DO. IT'S NICE, AND...

00:54.150 --> 00:55.378
MAYBE SOMEDAY,

00:55.420 --> 00:57.945
BUT I DON'T KNOW,
THE IDEA OF A CLEAN BREAK,

00:57.990 --> 00:59.480
IT JUST MAKES SO MUCH SENSE.

00:59.520 --> 01:01.852
- I KNOW.

01:04.230 --> 01:06.357
- I HAVE AN IDEA.

01:06.400 --> 01:11.167
HOW ABOUT IN TEN YEARS,
WE MEET RIGHT BACK HERE,

01:11.200 --> 01:12.633
SAME TIME, 4:00.

01:12.670 --> 01:14.399
AND IF WE'RE BOTH MARRIED,
GREAT.

01:14.440 --> 01:16.658
WE'LL TALK ABOUT OUR KIDS,

01:16.710 --> 01:20.498
BUT IF WE'RE BOTH SINGLE,
WE'LL GO FOR COFFEE,

01:20.540 --> 01:22.474
SEE WHERE IT GOES.

01:22.510 --> 01:24.944
- BOTH PRACTICAL
AND HUGELY ROMANTIC.

01:24.980 --> 01:26.049
