01:26.080 --> 01:27.843
- WELL...

01:27.880 --> 01:33.182
[boarding announcement
on P.A.]

01:33.220 --> 01:35.780
ALL RIGHT.

01:49.640 --> 01:50.902
- THERE'S ONLY ONE PROBLEM.

01:50.940 --> 01:52.601
TEN YEARS IS TOO LONG.

01:52.640 --> 01:54.369
- WELL, HOW ABOUT EIGHT?

01:54.410 --> 01:55.502
- HOW ABOUT SEVEN?

01:55.540 --> 01:57.940
- SEE YOU THEN.

