04:28.330 --> 04:29.866
BECAUSE NOW YOU KNOW,

04:29.900 --> 04:31.629
AND IT'S JUST GONNA MAKE YOU
A BETTER COP

04:31.670 --> 04:35.128
TO REALIZE THAT ALL PEOPLE
ARE ESSENTIALLY JUST OUT THERE

04:35.170 --> 04:38.606
