OF REAL CASES.

06:06.930 --> 06:09.967
- I KNOW. I'M--I JUST LOST
MY HEAD FOR A SECOND.

06:10.000 --> 06:11.262
I'M SORRY, CHIEF.

06:11.300 --> 06:12.631
- I DON'T MEAN TO SOUND
LIKE A HARD-ASS.

06:12.670 --> 06:13.637
- YOU DIDN'T.
- I DID.

06:13.670 --> 06:14.864
- I DIDN'T GET THAT AT ALL.

06:14.900 --> 06:16.401
- ACTUALLY, I WAS TRYING
TO SOUND LIKE A HARD-ASS.

06:16.440 --> 06:17.407
- MISSION ACCOMPLISHED.

06:17.440 --> 06:19.806
- GO BACK TO WORK, O'HARA.

06:24.310 --> 06:27.108
