06:54.240 --> 06:55.434
YOU.

06:55.480 --> 06:56.549
- WHY NOT SHAWN?

06:56.580 --> 06:58.241
- WELL,
IT'S A TRICKY SITUATION.

06:58.280 --> 06:59.816
SEE, IT'S SOMEBODY
THAT I USED TO KNOW.

06:59.850 --> 07:02.171
A BOYFRIEND--
WELL, A FORMER BOYFRIEND,

07:02.220 --> 07:03.949
