- NO.
NO, I DIDN'T KNOW THAT.

07:13.160 --> 07:15.048
- SHAWN WILL NEVER FIND OUT.

07:30.150 --> 07:31.742
- [slurps]

07:31.780 --> 07:32.872
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

07:32.920 --> 07:34.069
- WORKING ON A CASE
FOR JULIET,

07:34.120 --> 07:35.576
A RANDOM MISSING PERSONS CASE.

07:35.620 --> 07:36.939
