TO BOTHER YOU.

07:36.990 --> 07:38.787
- WHAT? JULES NEEDS HELP,
I'M IN. YOU KNOW THAT.

07:38.820 --> 07:41.050
- BUT NO--SHE SAID NO--
WELL, SAID NO.

07:41.090 --> 07:44.253
LOOK, I'D RATHER DO IT SOLO.

07:44.290 --> 07:45.655
- OH, MY GOD.

07:45.690 --> 07:47.920
ARE YOU IN THE VAULT OF SECRETS
RIGHT NOW?

07:47.960 --> 07:48.949
- NO.

07:49.000 --> 07:50.069
- YOU ARE.

07:50.100 --> 07:51.226
IT'S SE'I'I'LED.
I'M HELPING.

07:51.270 --> 07:52.999
- YOU ARE NOT HELPING.
