* IF IT'S ALL RIGHT

09:32.870 --> 09:34.792
* THEN YOU'RE ALL WRONG

09:34.840 --> 09:39.539
* BUT WHY BOUNCE AROUND
TO THE SAME DAMN SONG? *

09:39.570 --> 09:43.870
* YOU'D RATHER RUN
