- YOU CALLED YOUR DAD IN?

10:18.750 --> 10:20.672
- I WAS THE ONE WHO FOUND
THE GUY IN THE FIRST PLACE.

10:20.720 --> 10:22.472
- WHAT?
- WITH MY HELP.

