10:34.330 --> 10:37.219
SCO'I'I' SEAVER WAS PRONOUNCED
DEAD 4 1/2 YEARS AGO, RIGHT?

10:37.270 --> 10:39.067
CAR TOTALED
ON A LONELY STRETCH OF HIGHWAY

10:39.100 --> 10:40.362
IN THE CALIFORNIA DESERT,

10:40.400 --> 10:41.867
WINDOWS DOWN.

10:41.900 --> 10:42.901
- SO?

10:42.940 --> 10:44.828
- SO IT WAS 42 DEGREES
THAT NIGHT.

10:44.870 --> 10:47.304
- MORE IMPORTANTLY, CARS DON'T
SUDDENLY BLOW UP ON THEIR OWN.

10:47.340 --> 10:48.739
THEY CERTAINLY DON'T BLOW UP
IN A WAY

10:48.780 --> 10:50.338
SO THERE'S NO TRACE
OF ANYTHING.

10:50.380 --> 10:51.506
- SO WHAT'S NEXT?

10:51.550 --> 10:53.541
- SO GLAD YOU ASKED,

10:53.580 --> 10:56.981
BECAUSE THE THING IS...AHEM.

10:57.020 --> 10:58.487
[whispering] I MANAGED TO GET
ONTO A WEBSITE

10:58.520 --> 11:00.078
THAT I PROBABLY
SHOULDN'T BE ON.

11:00.120 --> 11:02.315
- SHAWN, DON'T TELL ME YOU'RE
GOING ALL PETE TOWNSEND ON ME.

