- FAIRLY.
SANTA BARBARA.

11:49.270 --> 11:51.261
- ARE YOU SURE IT'S COOL FOR US
TO BE IN THE CHIEF'S OFFICE?

11:51.310 --> 11:53.733
- OF COURSE, IT IS.
I PRACTICALLY RUN THIS PLACE.

11:53.780 --> 11:54.974
- ALL RIGHT.

11:55.010 --> 11:57.001
- HIT THE DECK!

11:58.550 --> 12:00.518
[whispering]
IT'S THE BISCUIT LADY.

12:00.550 --> 12:01.778
