12:32.750 --> 12:34.308
- THAT WAS A DUDE.

12:34.350 --> 12:36.375
- THAT MUST HAVE BEEN
SOME CRAZY PICNIC.

12:36.420 --> 12:38.888
- SO THIS BUILDING
WAS WARING'S LEGITIMATE FRONT.

12:38.920 --> 12:41.582
