HARD.

12:47.160 --> 12:49.025
ONE OF US IS
GONNA HAVE TO GRILL JULIET

12:49.060 --> 12:50.664
ON HER DEAD BOYFRIEND.

12:50.700 --> 12:51.894
I NOMINATE YOU.

12:51.930 --> 12:53.795
- WAIT A SECOND. WE'RE GONNA
INTERROGATE HER NOW?

12:53.840 --> 12:55.796
HASN'T SHE BEEN
THROUGH ENOUGH ALREADY?

12:55.840 --> 12:57.660
- WE'LL ALL DO IT TOGETHER...

12:57.710 --> 12:59.564
VERY DELICATELY.

13:06.210 --> 13:07.541
- WHAT?

13:07.580 --> 13:12.608
- JULES, WE WERE THINKING, UM,
COLLECT IVELY,

13:12.650 --> 13:14.584
